{"tid":2068372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港考車都岸九九:o)","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T16:47:03.000Z","uid":40879,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d4bbc244dc13302d98d6428e2a3b3bc7768b2b","tid":2068372,"uid":40879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"今日考油塘 一路行個考官都冚埋張黃紙<br />\n心諗實冇死喇今次<br />\n點知入番考試中心俾個考官話<br />\n考官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你入彎踩低極力子好危險架喎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n心諗轉急彎要拖慢架車 又唔係斜路轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果咪再考多次囉 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好L貴呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor 1999"},{"pid":"dca52663b2ca25eac5785b74756ade62d239d0c0","tid":2068372,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"87dacab638d7f3e5512dd97b5d76de562c6f460a","tid":2068372,"uid":9193,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"咁真係你問題喎<br />\n入彎前應該控制好車速唔需要踩油或者剎車架喎<br />\n你又唔係轉波/停車 踩極力子做乜撚嘢？"},{"pid":"feb25667639fff8a62f21daea20f9f8a52d40ebf","tid":2068372,"uid":358333,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"考油塘邊撚個灣急撚到你要用極力子拖慢架車啊"},{"pid":"b585eedb279d6b37f4e31a2beb3e936cdfcaf08b","tid":2068372,"uid":344256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d4bbc244dc13302d98d6428e2a3b3bc7768b2b","tid":2068372,"uid":40879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"今日考油塘 一路行個考官都冚埋張黃紙<br />\n心諗實冇死喇今次<br />\n點知入番考試中心俾個考官話<br />\n考官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你入彎踩低極力子好危險架喎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n心諗轉急彎要拖慢架車 又唔係斜路轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果咪再考多次囉 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好L貴呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor 1999"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim